description: Manor Lords is a medieval strategy game featuring in-depth city building, large-scale tactical battles, and complex economic and social simulations. Rule your lands as a medieval lord – the seasons pass, the weather changes, and cities rise and fall.

name: Nordhold
description: Enemies are coming! Every decision matters: build your city, grow the economy, and prepare for enemy waves. Strengthen your defenses, adapt your strategy, and unleash your hero’s full potential. This unique Tower Defense will test your skills – are you worthy to claim a place at Valhalla?

name: Rules & Rodents
description: A puzzling adventure where you abuse the Rules set by your Rat captors! 📜🐀 Manipulate enemies and environments with the commanding power of Rules to escape!

name: Jumalien
categories: ['Multi-player', 'PvP', 'Shared/Split Screen PvP', 'Shared/Split Screen', 'Steam Achievements', 'Full controller support', 'Remote Play Together', 'Family Sharing']
description: The great Jumalien tournament enters its final phase, only the god of gods will emerge victorious. Embody a deity and hunt down your opponents to receive the supreme sacrament in this local multiplayer hack & slash!

name: CARAMBOLA
description: A VR educational puzzle game where players explore constellations from different cultures, solve escape room-style riddles, and apply real-world knowledge to progress. Designed to promote cultural awareness through immersive, hands-on learning.

name: Locked in Temptation
description: Locked in Temptation is a choice-driven adult Visual Novel. Unravel the web of intrigue that threatens everything. Romance captivating women, uncover betrayals, and embrace your transformation in this thrilling blend of drama, intrigue, and sex.

name: Mojika - Truth Rears Its Ugly Head
description: Haunted by the ability to read minds, Suteru embarks on a journey of revenge against those who wronged him. Uncovering the secrets of his tormentors, he must confront his demons in a story that explores the depths and darkness of the human mind.

name: Pub Sim
description: You've just bought your first Pub. First steps are to clean it, stock it, set your markup and let in the Patrons. Keep the drinks flowing and try not to shortchange anyone! If you keep it going long enough you might just earn enough to spruce up the place, hire staff and expand the premises.

name: ファイヤーエムブレイスII～中年と希望の光～
description: ファイヤーエムブレイスII～中年と希望の光～ is a single player, the 1990s style game. The pixel art and retro BGM makes you nostalgic. Finally your goal is to reach a map where has the demon castle. Explore lots of maps and progress the story, and then defeat the demon king.

name: Space Sprouts
description: Launch into a chaotic spaceship adventure: bend the rules of physics, experiment with unusual gadgets and toss everything around. With each journey, you will have limited time to reveal the mysteries aboard your solar punk spaceship - how much will you discover before you arrive home?

name: So to Speak
description: Can you learn Japanese by solving puzzles? So to Speak is a game about wandering in Japan, looking at signs, overhearing conversations, and using context clues in the environment to figure out what it all means. No background in Japanese is assumed.

name: ROLLING STAR
description: Bursting with hilarious dialogue and comical encounters! The second installment of the super-exhilarating Metroidvania series is here!!

name: Siege Island
description: Step into the world of Siege Island, a tribute to the classic arcade game "Rampart". Prepare yourself for an immersive 3D action-puzzle game that will test your strategic skills and reflexes. As the Orcish fleet draws near, the duty to safeguard your island from their assaults is yours.

name: One Million Stars
categories: ['Single-player', 'Multi-player', 'Co-op', 'Shared/Split Screen Co-op', 'Shared/Split Screen', 'Remote Play Together', 'Family Sharing']
description: A chaotic ballet of color, a face-melting symphony of laser light action, an epic quest to infinity with 4 characters, unlockable ships, and local co-op. Old school arcade gameplay meets roguelike replayability in a psychedelic fever dream. Hold onto your butts, it’s a long way to ONE MILLION STARS.

name: Deconstruction Simulator: Prologue
description: Deconstruction Simulator: Prologue is the ultimate demolition simulator, offering you complete freedom of action and a wide array of contracts to complete. Get ready for spectacular destruction.

name: Einstein's Cats
description: A cozy, relaxing puzzle game all about cats. Solve brain-twisting logic clues to sort picky cats into their favorite boxes. Unlock stickers as you play to use in your Sticker-book to create your own cute cuddly cat scenes!

name: Comet Rogue

name: Project 0.1
description: Project 0.1 is a fast-paced, roguelike action game inspired by Vampire Survivors. With 15 unique skills to unlock and evolve, you must experiment with different builds to survive relentless enemy waves. How long can you survive the chaos?

name: Pull Stay
description: Pull Stay is a wacky Beat 'em up game with Tower Defense mechanics. Use your fists or set crazy traps to repel enemies from rushing into your house! As a guardian robot, defend your buddy Susumu who has been a shut-in for years!

name: ProtoDungeon: Episode I

name: Escape from Mutation Station
description: A short, unconventional escape room experience. You are the candidate. You must find a way out of this room. Things are not as they seem.

name: Robotic Arm Simulator
description: Control real-time physical simulation control and transform into a robotic arm operator. Challenging millimeter level grasping tasks in multiple precision industrial scenarios, any operational jitter could trigger a chain of disasters!

name: Vault of Power

name: Maximum Chaser : 1001 Squad

name: Merchant 64

name: Monster Hunter Wilds
